[[Spamhaus]] is one of the most reputable and accurate [[DNS-based blacklists]] used to [[combat spam]].

Their [http://www.spamhaus.org/sbl/index.lasso SBL Advisory] is "free for individuals operating small mail servers as long as your email traffic is low". Their [http://www.spamhaus.org/xbl/index.lasso XBL advisory] is also free for users with "normal mail servers". [http://www.spamhaus.org/datafeed/index.html Paid yearly subscriptions] are available for other users not falling into these categories.

